    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I asked for political asylum it took time, but one day, I knew when I was in Washington, I learned English much better, and I-- I got friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them was working as a secretary for a Senator Saltonstall from Massachusetts-- oh, from Massachusetts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he called me up and said, Gregory, you're-- you're authorized-- you're becoming citizen by the Congress, because he saw the papers, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, after a time, they called me and I-- I got my citizenship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I am.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
